.TH a3db 1 "February 2026" "arma-tools" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
a3db \- build and query an Arma PBO SQLite index
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B a3db
.RI [ flags ]
.RI [ output.db ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B a3db
scans game PBO archives and stores indexed metadata in a SQLite database for fast lookup.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI "-config " path
Load game directories from a JSON config file.
.TP
.BI "-arma3 " dir
Set Arma 3 directory.
.TP
.BI "-workshop " dir
Set Steam Workshop directory.
.TP
.BI "-ofp " dir
Set OFP / Arma: Cold War Assault directory.
.TP
.BI "-arma1 " dir
Set Arma: Armed Assault directory.
.TP
.BI "-arma2 " dir
Set Arma 2 directory.
.TP
.BI "-db " path
Set database file path.
.TP
.B
-ondemand
Skip eager P3D/PAA/audio parsing.
.TP
.BI "-find " pattern
Search indexed files by glob pattern.
.TP
.B
-info
Show database statistics.
.TP
.B
-update
Run incremental update for changed PBOs.
.TP
.B
--pretty
Pretty-print JSON output for
.BR -find .
.TP
.BR -h , " --help"
Show help.
.SH MODES
Build mode is default. Additional modes are enabled with
.BR -update ,
.BR -find ,
or
.BR -info .
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR pbo_info (1),
.BR pbo_extract (1)
